rows.label: qst700904_msg0001
rows.name:
Thanks for all your efforts!
Well? Have you found anything?

rows.label: qst700904_msg0002
rows.name:
We found some tracks, but we
hit a dead end while following them.

rows.label: qst700904_msg0003
rows.name:
Is there any chance that what you saw
wasn't a human, but a monster...?

rows.label: qst700904_msg0004
rows.name:
Huh?
Wait, over there... Who's that?!

rows.label: qst700904_msg0006
rows.name:
N-no!
I will not fall for the same trick twice.
There is no such thing as ghosts!

rows.label: qst700904_msg0012
rows.name:
We'll be fine!
If there's one thing we're good at,
it's stuff like this.

rows.label: qst700904_msg0013
rows.name:
Then it seems we're more alike than
I thought!

rows.label: qst700904_msg0014
rows.name:
Please hold the post for me awhile!
And no dying on the job, you hear?
